thread.title: Colombia to issue US dollar bonds due 2026: SEC filing
thread.title_full: Colombia to issue US dollar bonds due 2026: SEC filing | Reuters

author: Davide Scigliuzzo
title: Colombia to issue US dollar bonds due 2026: SEC filing
text: NEW YORK, Sept 21 (IFR) - The Republic of Colombia plans to issue new US dollar-denominated bonds due 2026 via Bank of America Merrill Lynch and Credit Suisse, according to a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission on Monday. (Reporting by Davide Scigliuzzo; Editing by Marc Carnegie)
